message: "If you use this software in your research or production systems, please cite it using the metadata below."
type: software
title: "RAG Financial Multimodal"
abstract: >
  Enterprise-grade multimodal RAG system for financial document analysis.
  Ingests PDFs (10-K, 10-Q, earnings releases) with vision-language chart extraction,
  hybrid RRF retrieval, cross-encoder reranking, numeric guardrails, PII redaction,
  multi-tenancy, and full OpenTelemetry observability.
